name: DJ Tameil
description: '''Tameil Paynes''' (known by his stage name '''DJ Tameil''') is an American [[disc jockey]] and [[record producer]] from [[Newark, New Jersey]]. He is credited with pioneering the [[Jersey club]] style of dance music in the late 1990s, drawing influence from [[Baltimore club]] and [[Chicago house]]. He is a member of the Brick Bandits, a collective of pioneering Newark musicians.
